title: Merriam-Websters Advanced Learners English Dictionary.bgl
description:
Merriam-Webster's Advanced Learner's English Dictionary.bgl


"Outstanding features include nearly 100,000 words and phrases, more than 160,000 usage examples, more than 22,000 idioms, verbal collocations, and commonly used phrases, and more than 1,000 original drawings--including 16 pages of full color art. Abundant supplemental information includes 25 pages of grammar."


Works with : GoldenDict, StarDict and Babylon etc.

You need any of the above mentioned programs to use this dictionary. Doesnot work standalone
